info.author: OpenDaylight Spectrometer Project
info.description: The main purpose of Spectrometer is to deliver transparent statistics of contributions to OpenDaylight Project. It collects activity data such as 1. commits and number of code lines changed from ODL Git repositories, 2. reviews from Gerrit, or 3. activities related to each project from mailing lists and presents the statistics in a user-friendly manner.
